Humation Flutter

This project is a Dart and Flutter port of Humation.

Engine design and the humation-1 asset set (86 SVG parts + manifest) are from:
  humation-labs/humation            https://github.com/humation-labs/humation (MIT)

The native rendering approach (SVG subset parsed to vector paths and composited,
no web view) follows:
  humation-labs/humation-swift       https://github.com/humation-labs/humation-swift (MIT)

The bundled humation-1.json in packages/humation_assets_humation_1 is taken
verbatim from the humation-swift resource, which was generated from
@humation/assets-humation-1. Selection hashing (FNV-1a over UTF-16 code units)
is byte-identical to the reference engine so the same seed yields the same
avatar on web, native, and Flutter.
